+++Cyndro Cledar+++

A few shots hit the Element's sheilds, but Cyndro just returned fire and 
fired a whole lot of laser shots at Cyclone and Scourge. The outside of the 
element was slowly growing out. The nanobots were slowly eating apart the 
Cybertronian Fire and building Maximal City around the Element. The room 
where they had come in through the underside was now totaly gone, and they 
were quickly taking more from the ship. They would take the shield making 
thingies as soon as the shields ran out, and then repower them and use them 
in the Element.


Cledar saw Motormaster driving up. He carefully took aim and fired his 
fusion cannon right at Motormaster's front. The huge blast streamed out 
toward the big vehicle, and Cledar looked to see if it had hit.
